Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要送給他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻拿不出勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶豫不決的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 情人節
